parts.text:
```json
{
  "application": "Meso-NH",
  "details": {
    "software": [
      "Mpirun",
      "cat",
      "ln",
      "scp",
      "ssh",
      "sbatch",
      "squeue",
      "bc"
    ],
    "resource_requirements": {
      "core": "CORE (default: 24)",
      "ncpus": "NCPUS (default: CORE)",
      "mpiprocs": "MPIPROCS (default: CORE)",
      "nbnodes": "NBNODES (calculated based on NBP and NCPUS)",
      "time": "TIME (default: 3600)",
      "jobout": "JOBOUT (default: Sortie_${NBP}P_${CORE}C_${NBNODES}N_${VER_MPI}.%j)",
      "jobname": "JOBNAME (default: job_${CONFEXP})"
    },
    "execution_environment": {
      "indir": "INDIR (default: INDIR)",
      "outdir": "OUTDIR (default: ${INDIR})",
      "subdir": "SUBDIR (default: ${PWD}/${CONFEXP})",
      "execdir": "EXECDIR (default: /tmpdir/${USER}/${CONFEXP})"
    },
    "transfer_protocol": {
      "inhost": "INHOST (default: local)",
      "outhost": "OUTHOST (default: ${INHOST})",
      "getfiles": "GETFILES (default: ln -s, scp, or ln -s depending on INHOST)",
      "putfiles": "PUTFILES (default: mv, scp, or cp depending on OUTHOST)",
      "rmmindir": "RMINDIR (default: ${INDIR}, ${INHOST}:${INDIR}, or ${INDIR} depending on INHOST)",
      "rmmkkdir": "RMMKDIR (default: mkdir -p, ssh ${OUTHOST} mkdir -p, or mkdir -p depending on OUTHOST)",
      "rmoutdir": "RMOUTDIR (default: ${OUTDIR}, ${OUTHOST}:${OUTDIR}, or ${OUTDIR} depending on OUTHOST)"
    }
  }
}
```
